## Limitations

The research is limited by the availability of online resources and the potential bias in historical interpretations. Some sources may not provide a comprehensive view of the lived experiences of enslaved individuals. Additionally, the lack of primary sources from the perspective of the enslaved limits the depth of understanding of their personal experiences and struggles.